text.section:
The council shall:
Elect its own chairperson and establish other officers and subcommittees as needed to execute the duties of the council;
Adopt bylaws and operate under its bylaws;
Select the director of the office;
Establish and evaluate goals and outcomes for the office that may facilitate treatment and care of persons with dementia;
Assist with the dissemination of information about the availability of program materials, education materials, and curriculum guides; and
Prepare a report of its activities, at least annually, for submission to the office.
